---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Tony from '../assets/tony.png';
---
<div class="container">
    <Image src={Tony} alt="" class="img"/>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="title">Fun, Stark-Inspired Coin</div>
        <div class="text">
            $TONY memecoin for $TON, created in Memepad BLUM. The main goal is to create a strong community on the telegram social network. $TONY will develop together with $TON, becoming more stable and in demand every year.
        </div>
        <div class="text">
            In the 1st quarter of 2025, $TONY will strive to become the most popular memecoin Memepad BLUM. With the help of $TONY, BLUM users will be able to trade and earn Meme Points (MP) and BLUM points without fear.
        </div>
        <div class="text">
            After BLUM's listing, $TONY will continue to occupy a place in the hearts of the community, bringing a lot of interesting events and fun.
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style scoped>
    .img {
        width: 700px;
        height: 660px;
        object-fit: contain;
        @media (max-width: 1000px) {
			width: 220px;
            height: auto;
		}
    }
    .content {
        max-width: 720px;
    }
    .container {
        width: 100%;
        margin: 50px 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 50px;
        padding:  0 12px;
        max-width: 1600px;
        @media (max-width: 1000px) {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
    }
    .title {
        font-size: 44px;
        margin: 0 8px;

        color: aliceblue;
        @media (max-width: 1000px) {
			font-size: 32px;
		}
    }
    .text {
        font-size: 22px;
        margin: 15px 8px;
        @media (max-width: 1000px) {
			font-size: 18px;
		}
    }
</style>